data.description:
Beautiful 2 story with 3 car garage in quiet cul-de-sac.  Walk in closet in Master, main floor laundry, Pergo floors, great vaulted ceilings. A must see!  You won't find a better house for the money in Westwoods Ranch.

Neighborhood Description

Small, quiet, family neighbohood.  Great neighbors!  Walking distance to bike/running trails, open space and golf course. Convenient to shopping, city and mountains.
